{"tid":771091,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"HKU太令我失望了","createTime":"2018-08-07T15:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T03:54:12.000Z","uid":187524,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"63435b4e8065bfc66dde8fff051191e913c0259e","tid":771091,"uid":187524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"點解港大可以咁勢利<br />\n明明大學就係一個比人去探索同了解知識嘅地方<br />\n而家一句無人讀就成個學科分拆<br />\n就算呢堆冷門科無人讀<br />\n大學都有責任繼續將知識傳承比下一代<br />\n更何況港大一年收咁多內地學生<br />\n賺埋都夠cover冷門科嘅operating cost<br />\n<br />\n難怪香港無人才<br />\n真係自己人逼走自己人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2R5e-6eC-t0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2R5e-6eC-t0&d=yGo76tklT05MsZmyErET3Izu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=69b66520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2R5e-6eC-t0</a>"},{"pid":"17db257241aae0af55085e69ecb4f93f15bbf388","tid":771091,"uid":45772,"like":19,"dislike":10,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"Should blame the society rather than the university."},{"pid":"cc201ea7445e6866c11e9a0789e16347a25bba9e","tid":771091,"uid":112551,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"好多大學都變晒質"},{"pid":"103c750e21d766a66c533742390f0880451e789d","tid":771091,"uid":187524,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"17db257241aae0af55085e69ecb4f93f15bbf388","tid":771091,"uid":45772,"like":19,"dislike":10,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"Should blame the society rather than the university."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"社會畸形唔代表大學要隨波逐流<br />\n大學正正就係一個最好嘅地方<br />\n比年青一代了解平常難以接觸嘅知識<br />\nEg 天文學<br />\n唔通因為天文學係非社會主流知識<br />\n所以大學就無必要開呢科?"},{"pid":"4b2dd7138006aa1a1363ce07c8d4785bd1cdf5e3","tid":771091,"uid":187524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc201ea7445e6866c11e9a0789e16347a25bba9e","tid":771091,"uid":112551,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T1